### Variables
@headChefId = 1

### Get all dishes
GET {{url}}/dishes

### Get all active dishes
GET {{url}}/dishes?active=true

### Get all inactive dishes
GET {{url}}/dishes?active=false

### Get dishes by station
GET {{url}}/dishes?stationId=1

### Get active dishes for station
GET {{url}}/dishes?stationId=1&active=true

### Get dish by id — check station shape in response
GET {{url}}/dishes/1

### Search by name
GET {{url}}/dishes/search?query=laks

### Get dishes grouped by station
GET {{url}}/dishes/grouped

### Get available dishes for week 7 2026
GET {{url}}/dishes/available?week=7&year=2026

### Create dish
POST {{url}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Røget Laks",
    "descriptionDA": "Laks med dildcreme og rugbrødschips",
    "stationId": 1,
    "allergenIds": [1, 2]
}

### Update dish — bilingual language
PUT {{url}}/dishes/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Opdateret Laks",
    "descriptionDA": "Opdateret beskrivelse",
    "nameEN": "Updated Salmon",
    "descriptionEN": "Updated description",
    "allergenIds": [1]
}

### Update dish — remove all allergens
PUT {{url}}/dishes/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

{
    "nameDA": "Opdateret Laks",
    "descriptionDA": "Opdateret beskrivelse",
    "allergenIds": []
}

### Activate dish e
PATCH {{url}}/dishes/1/activate
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

### Deactivate dish
PATCH {{url}}/dishes/1/deactivate
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}

### Delete dish — expect 204
DELETE {{url}}/dishes/2
X-Dev-User-Id: {{headChefId}}
